### System and Utility Endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:8000

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@apiVersion = v1
@accessToken = your_access_token_here

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### 2. API Documentation (Swagger UI)
GET {{baseUrl}}/docs

###

### 3. ReDoc Documentation
GET {{baseUrl}}/redoc

###

### 4. OpenAPI Schema
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi.json

###

### 5. Get Available Languages
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/language/

###

### 6. Set Language Preference (English)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/language/set
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "language": "en"
}

###

### 7. Set Language Preference (Japanese)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/language/set
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "language": "jp"
}

###

### 8. Set Invalid Language
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/language/set
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "language": "invalid"
}

###

### 9. Test Error Handling (404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/nonexistent

###

### 10. Test Error Handling (Method Not Allowed)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### 11. Test Error Handling (Invalid JSON)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/language/set
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "language": "en"
    "invalid": "json"
}

###

### 12. Test CORS Headers
OPTIONS {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/users/
Origin: http://localhost:3000

###
